      "span_text": "As we have mapped YY1 binding site on AKT to the PH domain ( Figure 3E and F) , we predicted that YY1 and PIP3 may compete in binding to AKT. This prediction was borne out by our observation that YY1 showed reduced interaction with AKT tagged by a myristoylation (myrist) sequence that promotes AKT association with PIP3/membrane  (Figure 4D )."
